I really tried to hear &quot;SWEET LOVE&quot; and then &quot;SHIRT&quot; but I don&#39;t hear the
vowel &#39;t&#39; in sweet nor do I hear the vowel &quot;t&quot; in SHIRT.  I definitely hear
SWEEP and SURE.  Although everyone hears differently and uses different
software and headphones/speakers to listen, sometimes it is a really good
file and I believe Steve was correct that this is a really excellent example
of immediate response.  But that&#39;s just my opinion which carries as much
weight as air LOL.



Kristin 


